OL,3,C'Environmental catastrophe' fears
OL,4,Cafter plastic pellets wash up on beach
OL,6,FA huge clean-up operation is under way
OL,7,Fafter a large quantity of plastic
OL,8,Fpellets washed up on a beach in East
OL,9,FSussex.
OL,11,FRother District Council said the
OL,12,Fpellets, commonly known as biobeads or
OL,13,Fnurdles, had come ashore in Camber on
OL,14,FThursday, and they were working to
OL,15,Fdetermine the scale of the incident.
OL,17,FThe authority said it was "not aware
OL,18,Fof any concerns regarding public
OL,19,Fhealth" but advised dog owners to keep
OL,20,Fthem under supervision to stop them
OL,21,Feating the pellets.
