OL,3,C'Environmental catastrophe' fears
OL,4,Cafter plastic pellets wash up on beach
OL,6,F"It's unclear where the pollution has
OL,7,Fcome from and investigations are
OL,8,Fongoing," a council spokesperson said.
OL,10,FLocal environmental groups and
OL,11,Fvolunteers have been working alongside
OL,12,Fthe Environment Agency and the council
OL,13,Fto clear up the spillage as best they
OL,14,Fcan.
OL,16,FThe Strandliners charity, which
OL,17,Fmonitors pollution along the south
OL,18,Fcoast, says it's one of the worst
OL,19,Fincidents they have ever seen, and
OL,20,Fwarned the pellets were catastrophic
OL,21,Ffor marine life.
