OL,3,C'Environmental catastrophe' fears
OL,4,Cafter plastic pellets wash up on beach
OL,6,FThey are asking local people to check
OL,7,Fneighbouring beaches for signs of
OL,8,Fbiobeads, to assess the extent of the
OL,9,Fspread.
OL,11,FMP for Hastings and Rye Helen
OL,12,FDollimore said she would be putting
OL,13,Fpressure on Southern Water to explain
OL,14,Fhow the biobeads got into the marine
OL,15,Fsystem.
OL,17,FThe plastic nurdles are commonly used
OL,18,Fby water treatment plants as part of
OL,19,Fthe sewage cleaning process.
