OL,3,C'Environmental catastrophe' fears
OL,4,Cafter plastic pellets wash up on beach
OL,6,FA Southern Water spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are working closely with the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency and Rother District
OL,9,FCouncil to investigate the source of
OL,10,Fplastic beads which have washed up on
OL,11,FCamber Beach, this investigation work
OL,12,Fis ongoing.
OL,14,F"Rother District Council is leading
OL,15,Fthe clean-up of the beach, using
OL,16,Fspecialists with a vehicle with
OL,17,Fsuction equipment to remove the beads.
OL,18,FWe are also supporting with the clean-
OL,19,Fup."
